summary: For if you don\'t like certain monsters.
descriptionHtml:
Skyrim Monster Mod Additions - Replacers
========================================

[center][img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/imageshare/images/2570251-1334782094.png[/img][/center]
[center][img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/imageshare/images/2570251-1334782031.png[/img][/center]

Description:

This mod is a series of files that gives you the option to switch one or several of the creatures from Skyrim Monster Mod back to vanilla.
Momod adds many new creatures to the game but you may want some of them to appear in your playthrough, just download the file with the name of the creature and place it in your data directory.


Requirements: 

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35631//?]Skyrim Monster Mod[/url]


Installation:

Unpack the zipped file into Steam\\Steamapps\\Common\\Skyrim\\Data,  To uninstall just remove mesh, use the folder structure to track it down.  One the mesh is removed the creature should revert back to the MoMod version.
author: Ironman5000
